% Statics of linear λ-calculus
%------------------------------------------------------%

inductive Oft : (Ψ:tctx) [Ψ ⊢ lctx] → [Ψ ⊢ tm] → [ ⊢ tp] → ctype =
| Oft/var : LkupExh [Ψ ⊢ Δ] [Ψ ⊢ #p] [ ⊢ T]
  → Oft [Ψ ⊢ Δ] [Ψ ⊢ #p] [ ⊢ T]
| Oft/lam :
  Oft [Ψ, x:tm ⊢ cons Δ[..] x T[] 𝟙] [Ψ, x:tm ⊢ M] [ ⊢ S]
  → Oft [Ψ ⊢ Δ] [Ψ ⊢ lam \x.M] [ ⊢ lolli T S]
| Oft/app : Oft [Ψ ⊢ Δ₁] [Ψ ⊢ M] [ ⊢ lolli T S]
	→ Oft [Ψ ⊢ Δ₂] [Ψ ⊢ N] [ ⊢ T]
	→ Merge [Ψ ⊢ Δ₁] [Ψ ⊢ Δ₂] [Ψ ⊢ Δ]
	→ Oft [Ψ ⊢ Δ] [Ψ ⊢ app M N] [ ⊢ S];